        {
          "children": [
            {
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "mode": "normal",
              "style": "",
              "text": "MAPS actively and comprehensively supports its Members, Associates, and partner networks transform their professional journey with strategic assistance designed for Muslim American public servants. Break through barriers and unlock your potential in government and civic leadership.",
