              "format": 0,
              "mode": "normal",
              "style": "",
              "text": "While many of our MAPS Academy offerings on navigating specific public service processes from the most junior internship and entry level placements to the most senior appointments and Senate confirmations remain internal and exclusive to members, MAPS releases several recorded sessions to the public.",
